03:35:37,439 --> 03:35:41,759
She dropped his foot in shock, and it 
knocked over the bowl with a crash.  

1757
03:35:42,800 --> 03:35:48,560
But as the servant started to shout to 
Penelope, Odysseus put his hand over her mouth.

1758
03:35:49,520 --> 03:35:57,121
'Say nothing, dear Eurycleia,' he 
whispered. 'No one in the palace can know.'

