While Telemachus asked Phemius for some music,  

2000
04:04:00,160 --> 04:04:03,680
Odysseus had a bath and put 
on some fine new clothes.  

2001
04:04:05,040 --> 04:04:11,519
Then Athene worked her magic on his appearance, 
giving him a younger face and a stronger body.  

2002
04:04:12,800 --> 04:04:16,880
When he went back to Penelope in 
the hall, he looked like a god.

2003
04:04:18,239 --> 04:04:21,679
'Well, Penelope, you are a strange woman.  

2004
04:04:22,640 --> 04:04:30,161
Few wives would stay out of their husbands' arms 
for as long as this. But I can wait. Eurycleia,  

2005
04:04:30,880 --> 04:04:36,720
please prepare a bed for me somewhere in the 
palace. I will be sleeping alone tonight.'

2006
04:04:37,760 --> 04:04:45,760
'You seem a strange man to me too. All these 
years I have carried a picture of you in my head.  

2007
04:04:46,880 --> 04:04:54,560
But you do not look like that picture. Come, 
Eurycleia, we must move the great bed that  

2008
04:04:54,560 --> 04:05:00,480
Odysseus himself built. Take it outside the 
bedroom and make it comfortable for him.'

2009
04:05:01,680 --> 04:05:08,320
This was Penelope's test for the man in 
front of her. He replied angrily, 'Lady,  

2010
04:05:09,279 --> 04:05:16,719
your words are like a knife in my heart. What 
have you done to our bed? I built it myself,  

2011
04:05:17,439 --> 04:05:21,599
using a tree that was growing in 
the palace as one of the bed's legs.

2012
04:05:22,399 --> 04:05:28,000
No one can move it - unless you have cut 
through the wood of the tree and destroyed it.'

2013
04:05:29,439 --> 04:05:35,839
At these words, Penelope's knees began 
to shake. No one knew the secret of  

2014
04:05:35,840 --> 04:05:41,120
the tree-bed except her husband and a 
servant who had died many years before.

2015
04:05:42,319 --> 04:05:48,799
'Do not be angry with me, Odysseus,' she 
cried. 'The bed is exactly as you left it.  

2016
04:05:49,680 --> 04:05:53,760
But I was so frightened that someone 
would come here pretending to be you.  

2017
04:05:54,880 --> 04:06:01,520
This was my test - and now I 
know. Husband, it is really you!'

2018
04:06:03,199 --> 04:06:07,679
She threw her arms around 
him. She was like a sailor  

2019
04:06:07,680 --> 04:06:14,720
whose ship has been destroyed in a storm. 
After swimming for many hours, he sees dry land  

2020
04:06:15,279 --> 04:06:21,120
and knows that he is saved. Penelope felt 
the same way about seeing her husband again.  

2021
04:06:22,239 --> 04:06:26,559
For a long time Odysseus and Penelope 
held each other, crying silently.

2022
04:06:27,840 --> 04:06:33,040
When everyone else in the palace had gone 
to bed, Odysseus finally broke the silence.  

2023
04:06:34,160 --> 04:06:41,040
'Dear wife, we have not yet come to the 
end of our troubles. On my journey home,  

2024
04:06:41,680 --> 04:06:44,000
I spoke with the prophet Teiresias.  

2025
04:06:44,960 --> 04:06:50,000
He told me that I had to make another long 
journey before I could enjoy a peaceful old age.'

2026
04:06:51,439 --> 04:06:58,000
Penelope questioned her husband about the details 
of this prophecy. 'If the gods have promised you  

2027
04:06:58,000 --> 04:07:05,439
a more peaceful old age,' she said finally, 'then 
there is hope that one day our troubles will end.'

2028
04:07:06,640 --> 04:07:12,161
Odysseus smiled at her words. 
Then he took his dear wife  to their bed.

2029
04:07:13,040 --> 04:07:16,800
- THE END -